title: Ep. - 441 - JENNIFER SAGINOR FROM SECRETS OF PLAYBOY ANDREEA NATALIA FROM JOE MILLIONAIRE
description:
Jennifer Saginor from Secrets of Playboy, an A&E docuseries which explores the hidden truths behind the fable and philosophy of the Playboy empire through a modern-day lens. Saginor is the author of Playground: A Childhood Lost Inside the Playboy Mansion.

 

Andreea Natalia from Joe Millionaire: For Richer or Poorer on Fox, which sends 20 women to France for a whirlwind romance with a man who they think is a dashing millionaire.
